CurrentWeek.description: Openinghours for the current week are returned. Similar to NextSevenDays with the difference that the first item will always be Monday.

NextSevenDays.description:
Openinghours for the next seven days are returned. Each result will contain the date and day-of-week. This will take into account any special
upcoming openinghours.

Regular.description: The regular openinghours for each day of the week will be returned without taking into account any special openinghours or holidays.
